    "body": "Thanks for your comments. I deliberately made the PR simplistic, to start the discussion.\n\nNow my question is, where do we check if the metadata is valid ?\nIt doesn't seem to be a good idea to put too much logic into a template. Should we simply pass the whole `nb.metadata` down to the highlighter and have it handle all corner cases ?\n"
  },
