    "body": "I agree there shouldn't be too much logic in templates. My first thought is that the exporter should set up a highlighter with the right lexer and output format, and register that as a filter for the template, so that in the template you can just do `highlight(code)`. But I haven't thought so much about the design of nbconvert, so there might be a way that makes more sense.\n"
